    "title": "[Perf] Improve fp8 quant in mla; replace ReduceSum with ReduceScatterSum",
    "user": {
      "login": "IwakuraRein",
      "id": 28486541,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI4NDg2NTQx",
